  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The main hypothesis is that performance of electroacupuncture before colonoscopy reduces pain
      during the exam.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      To assess the efficacy of pre-colonoscopic electroacupuncture in reducing discomfort during
      colonoscopy.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
